Hey guys, we've tracked down a cause of this bug and are working like mad to get it hotfixed out as soon as possible. We are testing a fix and doing our best to kill this bug with fire.

This is a super sucky bug, I'm sorry that this went out {{sticker:zombie-nunu-tears}}

EDIT: We've patched out a fix for the bug, please update if you're still running into it!

I'm experiencing this too. I have to then wait for the stupid dodge timer after restarting LoL. {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 
https://i.gyazo.com/df1b32ac35dca97c214ed1c92e1190f6.jpg

When is this going to be fixed? This is ridiculous.

Seriously Rito this needs to be fixed ASAP. Has happened to me in about a third of the games I have queued up for this afternoon... Waiting for my timer to expire now after the 4th. While some people are reporting that it doesn't happen until Summoner Spells are altered or skins are selected, Mine happens immediately upon entry into the Champ Select lobby. [](https://gyazo.com/a80bc30107072099366d393a78e3a2fb)

This is extremely frustrating.
